    Quickfix dangling hard links on cephfs volumes (#5682)
    
    This is a quickfix that forces a `stat` call after creating hard links.
    In a cephfs scenario this might be necessary in order to limit the
    amount of strayed inodes (see
    https://www.mail-archive.com/ceph-users@lists.ceph.com/msg53368.html).
